title: كم عدد الأخطاء الإملائية والنحوية يمكنك بقعة في النص؟
description:
Jill: […]lately I've been feeling sick a lot. Maybe I'm over training;[…] but I can't seem to lose any weight.
[…]
House: You have a parasite.
Jill: Like a tapeworm or something?
[…]
Jill: Can you do anything about it?
House: Only for about a month or so. After that it becomes illegal to remove […]
Jill: Illegal?
House: Don't worry. Many women learn to embrace this parasite. They name it, dress it up in tiny clothes, arrange playdates with other parasites…
Jill: Playdates?
House: It has your eyes.

options.text: Too many, my eyes are bleeding
